substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator” wherever appearing and struck out “and prepayment” after “advance” in par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/s423/a/9/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, § 423(a)(9)(B)","children":[],"tail":", (C), (b)(1)(A), substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator” wherever appearing, inserted “30,” before “32” in par. (3)(A), and in par. (3)(B) substituted “(B)” for “(B)(i)” and redesignated subcls. (I), (II), and (III) as cls. (i), (ii), and (iii), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/s423/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, § 423(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", as amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/86"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–86","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Secretary’s” for “Administrator’s” in par. (3)(B)(iii)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (c), (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/s423/b/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, § 423(b)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1982—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/295/s4/59/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–295, § 4(59)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1972-10-24"},"text":"October 24, 1972","children":[],"tail":"” for “after the effective date of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s1780"},"text":"section 1780 of this title","children":[],"tail":"” in par. (2), and struck out the comma after “or 35” in provisions following par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/295/s4/59/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–295, § 4(59)(B)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “of this title” after “provision of thi